index = Index(['field1.inner'], 'simple_inner_index', 'simple_id')
model = SimpleIndexInterface()
model.data['field1'] = {'inner': 'innerValue'}
index.put(model)
result = Database.get().get(

self.assertEqual(result['field1_inner'], 'innerValue')
